<section class="section ">
  <div>
    <div class="section__color-wrapper ">
      <div class="container "><div class="content-box content-box--large content-box--text-center content-box--center text-container"><h3 class="heading h2">INDESTRUCTIBLE</h3><p>The solar cells' flexibility and the robust ETFE coating make this portable solar charger virtually indestructible and extremely durable. </p><p>The solar panel integrated in the Zenit solar backpack does not fear shocks, scratches, dust, sand water or being bent, so it can follow you on all your adventures! </p><div class="button-wrapper">
              <a href="/pages/r-d" class="button button--primary">MORE ABOUT THE TECHNOLOGY</a>
            </div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</div><div id="shopify-section-template--19348577386841__022ee9d5-4f6d-459a-9d90-744796593695" class="shopify-section shopify-section--gallery"><style>
